fig_6021 <- 
  faithful %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = waiting)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 5, fill = "#FFFFFF", color = "#000000") +
  labs(subtitle = "binwidth = 5")

binsize = diff(range(faithful$waiting)) / 15

fig_6022 <- 
  faithful %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = waiting)) +

  labs(subtitle = "with 15 bins")
